request.description:
Create a new claude-code session.

Note: if the agent is not logged in, you will receive AUTH_REQUIRED with a login URL. Call POST /agents/claude-code/auth/login first.

Message body:
```json
{
  "id": "msg-001",
  "type": "session.create",
  "sessionId": "session-abc-123",
  "flow": "claude-code",
  "payload": {
    "connectionMode": "spawn",
    "workingDir": "/tmp/my-project",
    "model": "claude-sonnet-4-6"
  },
  "timestamp": "2026-03-21T00:00:00Z"
}
```

Success response:
```json
{
  "type": "session.created",
  "replyTo": "msg-001",
  "payload": {
    "sessionId": "session-abc-123",
    "flow": "claude-code",
    "status": "created",
    "capabilities": { "streaming": true, "toolUse": true, ... }
  }
}
```

Auth failure response:
```json
{
  "type": "error",
  "error": {
    "code": "AUTH_REQUIRED",
    "message": "AUTH_REQUIRED: agent \"claude-code\" is not logged in; visit https://claude.ai/oauth/authorize?..."
  }
}
```

List all active sessions (server-wide).

Message body:
```json
{
  "id": "msg-002",
  "type": "session.list",
  "sessionId": "session-abc-123",
  "flow": "claude-code",
  "payload": {},
  "timestamp": "2026-03-21T00:00:01Z"
}
```

Response:
```json
{
  "type": "session.list.result",
  "payload": {
    "sessions": [
      { "sessionId": "session-abc-123", "flow": "claude-code", "status": "running", "createdAt": "..." }
    ]
  }
}
```

Send a prompt to the agent. Receives a stream of events (stream.start → stream.delta × N → stream.end).

Message body:
```json
{
  "id": "msg-003",
  "type": "prompt.send",
  "sessionId": "session-abc-123",
  "flow": "claude-code",
  "payload": {
    "content": "Write a Go function that checks if a number is prime"
  },
  "timestamp": "2026-03-21T00:00:02Z"
}
```

Event stream:
```json
{"type":"stream.start"}
{"type":"agent.status","payload":{"status":"thinking"}}
{"type":"stream.delta","payload":{"contentType":"text","content":"Here's a Go function..."}}
{"type":"stream.end","payload":{"finishReason":"complete","usage":{"totalCost":0.002}}}
{"type":"agent.status","payload":{"status":"idle"}}
```

Request conversation history (claude-code only).

Message body:
```json
{
  "id": "msg-007",
  "type": "history.request",
  "sessionId": "session-abc-123",
  "flow": "claude-code",
  "payload": { "limit": 20 },
  "timestamp": "2026-03-21T00:00:05Z"
}
```

Response:
```json
{
  "type": "history.result",
  "replyTo": "msg-007",
  "payload": {
    "messages": [
      { "role": "user",      "content": "Write a prime checker..." },
      { "role": "assistant", "content": "Here's a Go function..." }
    ]
  }
}
```

